OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCanada indigenous          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchildren's compensation    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Forder upheld               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Canada's federal court has dismissed a 
OL,6, government bid to avoid paying         
OL,7, compensation to indigenous children who
OL,8, suffered welfare discrimination.       
OL,10,FIn 2016, a rights tribunal ruled that  
OL,11,Fthe government had underfunded First   
OL,12,FNations children's services compared   
OL,13,Fwith those for non-indigenous children.
OL,15,FIt ordered C$40,000 ($31,350; #23,340) 
OL,16,Fpayouts to each child forced to leave  
OL,17,Ftheir homes to access the services.    
OL,19,FWednesday's court ruling is expected to
OL,20,Fcost Ottawa billions of dollars.       
